reviewText:
RollerCoaster Tycoon is a game I have played since the early 2000, as I can remember anyway, although I mostly watched my sister play it, I would attempt to play now and then, but being the kid I was back then, of course it went straight down to no guests :D

Now, as I have gotten a tiny bit older, I finally get the guest bar up instead of down, and it really is nostalgia <3

For new players;
It isn't Call of Duty or InFlux,Tera or Skyrim, it doesn't have heavy graphics, but it really is a joy, or at least it'll make time fly.

For old players;
..I got nothing to say, if you miss this game, get it. Especially when there's a sale, no excuse :D

